00:17:45.560 --> 00:17:48.110
I just wanted to
make one more point,

00:17:48.110 --> 00:17:51.710
namely a picture is
worth a thousand words,

00:17:51.710 --> 00:17:54.500
but a spectrum is worth
a thousand pictures.

00:17:54.500 --> 00:17:57.570
Because this is a
star-- this is a picture

00:17:57.570 --> 00:18:01.015
of a very important star.

00:18:01.015 --> 00:18:02.390
But when you look
at the picture,

00:18:02.390 --> 00:18:04.060
it's a fuzzy blob
in the universe.

00:18:04.060 --> 00:18:06.152
How boring.

00:18:06.152 --> 00:18:07.110
It's incredibly boring.

00:18:07.110 --> 00:18:08.880
It doesn't really
