00:20:29.210 --> 00:20:32.272
So we can measure this
tiny little iron line here.

00:20:32.272 --> 00:20:33.230
And here's another one.

00:20:33.230 --> 00:20:37.590
This is the calcium line
here-- to do our work.

00:20:37.590 --> 00:20:39.570
So it's quite painstaking.

00:20:39.570 --> 00:20:43.340
And it takes years sometimes
