00:41:13.110 --> 00:41:15.260
That's actually
easy to remember.

00:41:15.260 --> 00:41:20.190
And so the guys that we
are interested in now

00:41:20.190 --> 00:41:22.620
have about 0.6 to
0.8 solar masses

00:41:22.620 --> 00:41:25.210
because they have total
lifetimes of 15 to 20

00:41:25.210 --> 00:41:26.380
billion years.

00:41:26.380 --> 00:41:30.650
So if they're formed
14 billion years ago,

00:41:30.650 --> 00:41:34.120
