to go, but not that long.

00:41:34.120 --> 00:41:36.900
And so they are just in the
right evolutionary state

00:41:36.900 --> 00:41:39.360
right now for us to find
them and to not have

00:41:39.360 --> 00:41:42.090
messed up their surfaces
from the interior

00:41:42.090 --> 00:41:45.990
and doing all sorts
of other wonky things.

00:41:45.990 --> 00:41:48.057
So yeah, it's kind of by design.

